Analysis of the outcome in surgical treatment of cancer of the organs of the pancreatoduodenal region. The surgical treatment results of the hepatopancreatoduodenal zone cancer in the clinic from 1987 till 1992 are adduced. Of 91 operated patients in 31 of them the radical or conditionally radical operations were done. The modifications of their own of conventional methods were applied. Further improvement of the diagnosis methods is needed as well as the search of possibilities to augment the frequency of the radical operations accomplishment.